{"type": "article", "id": 24966, "title": "不仔细看，这些人就被淹没在了宜家的背景里", "description": "一个摄影师的作品，她选择宜家是因为它是一种普遍的消费文化。", "date": "2016-04-06T07:19:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 2247, "name": "照片"}, {"id": 25852, "name": "消费文化"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 25830, "name": "Margeaux Walter"}], "category": 5, "author": 18, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 112, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607125544kYSv2dTCURrKbM7n.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">逛宜家是一种什么样的感觉？如果你也曾在催眠般、重复的产品间体会过一种迷失的感觉，艺术家 Margeaux Walter 的这组名为 <a href=\"http://www.margeauxwalter.com/art/projects/sign-language-excerpt\">Sign Language</a> 的摄影作品或许会让你产生共鸣。在这组照片中，消费者看上去好像失去了自己的个性，和背景中 Walter 购置的宜家产品融为一体。</p>\n<p class=\"\">所有场景都是她在自己的摄影棚里搭建的，然后她将哈苏（Hasselblad）相机架在一个长三脚架上俯拍出了这些照片。“我之所以选择宜家是因为它是个大部分人都熟悉的家居公司，不同国家、种族、阶级的人都能认出它来。” Walter <a href=\"http://lens.blogs.nytimes.com/2016/03/30/margeaux-walter-ikea-new-york-portfolio-review/\">表示</a>，“而且它也是消费文化的一种表现。”<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125539NOG3krxftjQTPuWE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《In Bloom》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125540tsIeQU6HTG0XLaAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13149171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Borderline》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125540pI6yf2ZJCzVMo15r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71386719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Checkmate》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125541U15t9XPNDRiQJY3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Cocoon》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125541HUs37BIGviJtpAue.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.19906323\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《REM》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125542VsvY9wKTzc4pHaXu.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Patchwork》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125542jQZRshzx15f2EJe6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Red Dot》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125543ejEUdzCSfNlhOHPK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.29814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Static》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607125543guNyQGVBriYXOzC2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">《Primary》</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">不过，Walter 也并非用宜家商品进行创作的第一人。早在 2007 年，以色列艺术家 Guy Ben-Ner 就拍摄了一个名为 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U3yBQT9mfnw\">Stealing Beauty</a> （需科学上网）的视频。视频中，Ben-Ner 和他的妻子和孩子出现在世界各地的宜家展示空间当中，表演着半即兴的小短剧——直到工作人员介入，把他们赶走。<br></p>\n<p>Walter 现居美国纽约市，她在 2014 年获得了纽约城市大学亨特学院（Hunter College）的艺术硕士（M.F.A.）学位，Sign Language 正是她的硕士毕业作品。她的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/margeauxwalter/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Instagram</a> 是@margeauxwalter。</p>\n<p class=\"\">文中图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.margeauxwalter.com/art/\">Margeaux Walter</a></p>\n\n\n"}